If you are using Windows, make sure you have the necessary USB to UART driver isntalled:

Go Here: https://www.silabs.com/software-and-tools/usb-to-uart-bridge-vcp-drivers?tab=downloads#software

Download Link: https://www.silabs.com/documents/public/software/CP210x_Windows_Drivers.zip

Make sure you slect the x64 install version.

